// Hand-maintained village map. (Originally generated from the Tiled maps, but
// the generator was removed — edit the ASCII grids / doors directly here.)
// Collision lives in `groundLayer` (walkableGround) + `decoLayer` (solidDeco);
// both are ASCII grids (see src/world/asciiMap.ts):
//   ground:  ~ water   . grass   , dark grass   : path
//   deco:    . open    # solid
// The `baked` block is the verbatim Tiled render (GID arrays — don't hand-edit)
// and `objects`/`npcs`/`doors` are gameplay markers. To block a tile put a `#`
// in the deco grid; to add a door, push { cx, cy } and clear its deco cell.
// Note: solid cells over tree canopies / building roofs are auto-cleared at
// load by matchCollisionToSprites (village.ts) using each tileset's
// spriteRows/solidRows metadata below.
